      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
